Nature's Wrath in Full Fury!

Watch out for the vortex! It's a season of furious emerald storms and a sky alive with portents, as Pokemon and creatures from Ultra Space clash. Face the winds of change head-on in the Pokemon TCG: Sun & Moon - Celestial Storm!

Contents:
• 8 Celestial Storm booster packs
• 65 card sleeves featuring Rayquaza
• 45 Energy cards
• A player's guide
• 6 damage-counter dice
• Competition-legal coin-flip die
• 2 acrylic condition markers
• 1 acrylic GX marker
• A collector's box
• 4 dividers
• A Pokemon Trading Card Game Online code card
